					<td><span class="programlisting"><pre>background-position-x: [<span class="replaceable">percentage</span> | <span class="replaceable">length</span>] | [left | center | right ]background-position-y: [<span class="replaceable">percentage</span> | <span class="replaceable">length</span>] | [top | center | bottom]</pre>
						</span></td>
